    "description": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"/static/picture/hk30day-1.png\" alt=\"3日 6GB FUP\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">基本信息</div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">實名登記</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">《電訊（登記用戶識別卡）規例》（以下簡稱「《規例》」）已於2021年9月3日生效。根據該《規例》， 自2022年3月3日起，可於本地使用的預付儲值卡必須先完成實名登記才可啓用有關電訊服務。將實體SIM卡插入手機或將eSIM下載安裝至手機以完成實名登記後即可啟用服務。<a href=\"https://www.cuniq.com/global/HKRealNameRegistration\" target=\"_blank\"\r\n        >按此登記</a\r\n      ></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">數據用量</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">此卡提供6GB高速數據, 5G/4G網絡流動數據服務。 當於數據用量達到6GB「公平使用數據用量上限」，客戶仍可使用流動數據服務，但其數據傳輸速度將減慢及被控於512kbps，並且不可用於網絡分享及點對點傳輸 。需配備VoLTE功能的手機使用。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">可用日數</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">3日。啟用儲值卡當日起計之第3日(香港時間) 23:59終止。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <!-- <span  class=\"title_\">數據有效期</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">3日。</span> -->\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">有效期</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">自購買日起計一年內可啟用，逾期無效。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span  class=\"title_\">覆蓋地區</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">香港</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span  class=\"title_\">話音/短訊</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">不適用</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span  class=\"title_\">可否增值</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可增值。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span  class=\"title_\">啟用地點</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">香港</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span  class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal&nbsp;SIM&nbsp;三合一&nbsp;(適合各款手機)</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span  class=\"title_\">使用指南</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n\t     <span  class=\"title_\">eSIM</span>\r\n\t     <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\r\n\t </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"/static/picture/hk30day-1.png\" alt=\"3日 6GB FUP\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">Basic Information</div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Real-Name Registration</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">\r\n          The Telecommunications (Registration of SIM Cards) Regulation (“Regulation”) came into effect on 1st September 2021. Pursuant to the Regulation, prepaid SIM cards that can be used in Hong Kong must complete Real-Name Registration in order to activate or continue the use of telecommunications service from 1 March 2022. Insert the physical SIM card into your mobile phone or download and install the eSIM to your mobile phone to complete the Real-Name Registration and then activate the service. <a href=\"https://www.cuniq.com/global/HKRealNameRegistration\">Register Here</a> </span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Fair use of data</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">\r\n         The SIM card provides 6GB mobile data service,  5G/4G network. Once your total data usage reach \"Fair Usage Level (FUP)\" 6GB, the upload/download speed would be reduced and controlled at 512kbps and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available.Requires a mobile phone equipped with VoLTE function.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span  class=\"title_\">Data validity period</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">3-Day. The SIM card will be expired on the 3rd day at 23:59 Hong Kong time since card activation. </span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Validity period</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span  class=\"title_\">Coverage area</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Hong Kong</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span  class=\"title_\">Voice/SMS</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span  class=\"title_\">Whether add value</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span  class=\"title_\">Enable the location</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Hong Kong</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">SIM type</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、 Normal All-in-one SIM</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">User Guide</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\"\r\n        ><a\r\n          href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/services/travel-card-guide-n\"\r\n          target=\"_blank\"\r\n          >Click here to view</a\r\n        ></span\r\n      >\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\"\r\n        ><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\"\r\n          >Click here to view</a\r\n        ></span\r\n      >\r\n    </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
