    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20250722/tc/P0000944.png\" alt=\"8日 8+3GB FUP\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\n\t\tBasic Information\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Fair use of data </span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">The SIM card provides 11GB mobile data service,  5G/4G network. Once your total data usage reach \"Fair Usage Level (FUP)\" 11GB, the upload/download speed would be reduced and restricted(controlled at 256kbps) and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available.Requires a mobile phone equipped with VoLTE function.</span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Data validity period </span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">8-Day. The SIM card will be expired on the 5th day at 23:59 Hong Kong time since card activation. </span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Validity period</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span>\n\t</div>\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Real-Name Registration</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">No need</span>\n\t</div> -->\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Coverage area</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">Japan</span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Voice/SMS</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Voice/SMS storage value </span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Whether add value</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Enable the location</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">Japan</span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">SIM type </span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、 Normal All-in-one SIM</span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">User Guide</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">Click to\n\t\t\t\tview</a></span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">Click to view</ a></span>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
