    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"/static/picture/uscamexco30-chi.png\" alt=\"30日 Daily 1GB FUP\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\n        Basic Information\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Fair useuse of data</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">The SIM card provides 4G network mobile data service. Once your total data usage reach \"Fair Usage Level (FUP)\" 1GB, the upload/download speed would be reduced and restricted(minimum 512kbps) and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available.</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Data validity period</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">30-Day. Every 24 hours from the activation time is counted as one day, and any less than one hour is also counted as one hour, and is calculated in Hong Kong time.</span>\n    </div>\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Real-name Registration</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">Not required</span>\n    </div> -->\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Coverage area</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">USA, Canada, Mexico</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Whether add value</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span>\n    </div>\n\t\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Last activation date</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"value\">Please refer to the back of the packing</span>\n\t</div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Enable the location</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">USA, Canada, Mexico. Insert the SIM card into the mobile phone and the mobile network signal will be detected. This means the SIM card has been activated automatically and the service has been commenced. The validity period of the SIM card service starts from the day of activation and service commencement.</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">SIM type</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、 Normal All-in-one SIM</span>\n    </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
