    "description": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20240422/306.png\" alt=\"30日 3GB FUP\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\n        基本信息\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">數據用量</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此卡提供4G網絡流動數據服務。 當於數據用量達到3GB「公平使用數據用量上限」，客戶仍可使用流動數據服務，但其數據傳輸速度將被減慢及限制（但不低於512kbps），並且不可用於網絡分享及點對點傳輸 。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n      <span style=\"width: 110px\">可用日數</span>\n      <span class=\"value\">30日，以啟用時間起計每24小時為30日， 不足1小時亦以1小時計算，並以香港時間計算。</span>\n    </div>\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">有效期</span>\n        <span class=\"value\"> 30日，以啟用時間起計每24小時為30日， 不足1小時亦以1小時計算，並以香港時間計算。</span>\n    </div> -->\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地區</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">沙特阿拉伯、埃及及土耳其 </span>\n    </div>\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">話音/短訊</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">不適用</span>\n    </div> -->\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">話音/短訊儲值額</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">不適用</span>\n    </div> -->\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">可否增值</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可增值。</span>\n    </div>\n\t\t    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">最後啓用日期</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">請參考卡套上的日期</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">啟用地點</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">沙特阿拉伯、埃及及土耳其。但請注意SIMS卡插入手機並收到網絡訊號, 即已自動激活SIM卡並啟用服務。SIM卡服務之有效期由激活及啟用服當日起計。</span>\n    </div>\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">即買即用</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">\n               實體SIM卡插入電話後即可自動啟用；eSIM掃描激活二維碼後即可自動啟用。使用有效期亦已開始計算。\n            《電訊（登記用戶識別卡）規例》（以下簡稱「《規例》」）已於2021年9月30日生效，根據該《規例》，\n\t\t\t自2022年3月30日起，可於本地使用的預付儲值卡必須先完成實名登記才啓用有關電訊服務。\n\t\t\t</span>\n    </div> -->\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手機)</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">使用指南</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">實體SIM卡插入電話後即可自動啟用</span>\n    </div>\n\t<!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n  <span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span>\n  <span class=\"value\">不適用</span>\n  <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\n   </div> -->\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20240422/306.png\" alt=\"30日 3GB FUP\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\r\n        Basic information\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">Fair useuse of data</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">The SIM card provides 4G network mobile data service. Once your total data usage reach \"Fair Usage Level (FUP)\" 3GB, the upload/download speed would be reduced and restricted(minimum 512kbps) and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">Data validity period</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">30-Day. Every 24 hours from the activation time is counted as one day, and any less than one hour is also counted as one hour, and is calculated in Hong Kong time.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Validity period</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">Real-name Registration</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Not required</span>\r\n    </div> -->\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">Coverage area</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Saudi Arabia, Egypt & Turkey</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">Voice/SMS</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\r\n    </div> -->\r\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">Voice/SMS storage value</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\r\n    </div> -->\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">Whether add value</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Last activation date</span>\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"value\">Please refer to the back of the packing</span>\r\n\t</div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">Enable the location</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Saudi Arabia, Egypt & Turkey. Insert the SIM card into the mobile phone and the mobile network signal will be detected. This means the SIM card has been activated automatically and the service has been commenced. The validity period of the SIM card service starts from the day of activation and service commencement.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">SIM type</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、 Normal All-in-one SIM</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">User Guide</span>\r\n       <span class=\"value\">Insert the SIM card into the mobile phone and the mobile network signal will be detected.</span>\r\n\t\t</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n\t<!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n  <span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span>\r\n  <span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\r\n  <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">Click to view</a></span>\r\n   </div> -->\n</div>\n</div>",
